[FILE:275:descriptions/desc.primary]
Libcdio-paranoia is a port of Xiph.org's CDDA Paranoia that uses libcdio 
for CD-ROM access. The major benefit is better portability.

Paranoia is an Audio CD reader that aims for the highest accuracy 
possible. Audio is read directly as data with no analog step in between.


